data.name: Aether Dash
data.tooltip: Dashes towards a target location, dealing <d ref="duckiesHeroArchangelAirDash_Damage.amount" style="Bold"/> damage to enemy air units in its path and slowing them by <d ref="duckiesHeroArchangelAirDash_Debuff.modifiers[0].amount * (-1)"/>% for <d ref="duckiesHeroArchangelAirDash_Debuff.duration"/> seconds.
